caption: I've been wanting to meet my idols for 2 1/2 years and nothing I want more is to meet my idols and say thank you for always inspiring me to always believe in myself and never let anyone tell me different. I wish I could have met them in Boston but the stupid meet and greet got cancelled? please come back to Boston soon before you guys get too big? I love you guys with all my heart?? @JackandJackOfficial @JackGilinskyOfficial @JackJohnsonOfficial
